{"tid":462963,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩backpack好？","createTime":"2017-11-09T05:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T08:19:26.000Z","uid":119789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b090e6798c5c4ca690412c6d22108697ac3d7605","tid":462963,"uid":119789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"近排想轉個背囊<br />\n朋友都話arc&rsquo;teryx Arro22/Gregory day<br />\n<br />\nGregory中規中矩<br />\n面識跣水 又有個電腦位隔<br />\n<br />\n但arc&rsquo;teryx 有咩好？<br />\n都識跣水 但係個型上闊下尖<br />\n好似擺唔到啲咩<br />\n<br />\n各位ching仲有無咩好推介？<br />\n日常使用 會帶13吋電腦<br />\n間中都會行下山 想襟用啲<br />\n&lt;$2000<br />\n(聽講Gregory arc&rsquo;teryx 都用到三四年?)<br />\n<br />\n賜酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80a58d53e3212814c7e9ca842efc3bf5f84fcb8","tid":462963,"uid":72827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:19:26.000Z","msg":"Orspey, F/CE, Snow peak, Danton"}]}